  "KIRMIK Intelligent Video Analytics (KIVA) SoC is our company’s next and Al supported solution for smart city applications including an image processor (ISP) with 4k image processing capability, a 4 TOPS neural network processing engine (NPU), and a H.265 Video Codec. KIVA SoC is target to be manufactured on TSMC 22nm technology.",
  "ÇENTİK is a 32-bit RISC-V based microcontroller with peripherals like UART, SPI, I2C, PWM targeting low-cost control systems like home appliances, motor control, robotics, human machine interface. It is targeted to be manufactured on TSMC 55nm technology.",
