  "“DIGITAL TAG SYSTEM” project is aimed to completely prevent LOST, LEAK, STOLEN in all retail areas and especially in merchandising operations, and to carry out all operational activities online with information processing technologies.\nElectronic shelf label, is an e-ink display device mainly placed on the shelf-edge, that replaces the traditional paper price label are getting popular nowadays. Digital Tag System attaches these energy efficient displays to the security tags while improving their existing security functions and applying additional innovative operational capabilities to traditional tags. Every Digital Tag is connected to the DES database through wireless network and displays the latest price information of the items accurately in real time. Instantly meeting dynamic pricing needs such as instant campaigns, price changes, multiple purchase discounts, DES helps you renew your business model with its cloud-integrated shelf labeling system.",
